      "title": "Meeting between Minister of State for Energy of Qatar and Kanchana",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Kanchana Wijesekera, Minister of Power and Energy, who is on a visit to Qatar to discuss a number of issues, including the availability of fuel to Sri Lanka, has held discussions with the Minister of State for Energy and the Chief Executive of Qatar Energy, Saad Sheridan Al Kabi.",
        "With the support of Qatar Energy and the Qatar Development Fund to help ease the energy crisis in Sri Lanka, Petroleum Products, LPG And LNG. Obtained is discussed here."
      ],
